===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Originally {{zh-m|*丯}}, pictogram of something carved/engraved. The {{zh-m|*刀|knife}} component is added to indicate the tool, forming a {{Han compound|丯|刀|ls=psc|c1=p|c2=s|t2=knife|nocap=1}}.

Proto-form of {{zh-m|*契}}, and perhaps the proto-form of {{zh-m|*栔}}.

